{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Cool thing Thursday: iA Writer","content":"<p>Having had writing aspirations my whole life &#8211; started my first big awesome epic novel that&#8217;s going to be super awesome and everyone will want to read when I was 9 or 10 &#8211; I&#8217;ve gone through many writing tools.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 352px\" class=\"wp-caption alignright\"><img class=\"  \" title=\"Best writing tool\" src=\"http://distilleryimage6.s3.amazonaws.com/b5299ee41ef011e2979222000a1e9df0_7.jpg\" alt=\"Best writing tool\" width=\"342\" height=\"342\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Best writing tool</p></div>\n<p>First it was notebooks that never got filled beyond the first five pages. Then we got a computer and I used <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"WordPad\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WordPad\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">WordPad</a>, which was quickly usurped by <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Microsoft Word\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Word\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">MS Word</a> because it was <em>better</em>.</p>\n<p>I ended up playing with shiny fonts more than writing. Oh so many shiny fonts! Y&#8217;know I used to collect those &#8230;</p>\n<p>In high school I went back to notebooks, this time I managed to fill them up with terrible prose and even worse poetry. It was writing utopia.</p>\n<p>The thing about a notebook is that there&#8217;s nothing else. It&#8217;s just a notebook. Its purpose in life is providing a big surface that you can scribble upon with your favourite pen. There are no toolbars on the side, no chrome up top, it doesn&#8217;t even care about the font you&#8217;re using.</p>\n<p>A notebook doesn&#8217;t judge. There&#8217;s no <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Word count\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Word_count\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">word count</a>, no reliable page count, no structure.</p>\n<p>But notebooks really <em>really</em> <strong><em>really</em></strong><em></em> suck at editing.</p>\n<h2>Good writing, on computers</h2>\n<p>A few years ago I discovered <a href=\"http://www.hogbaysoftware.com/products/writeroom\" target=\"_blank\">WriteRoom</a>. Oh it was wonderful, finally my writing could cover the whole string and there was nothing to distract me from getting completely lost in the words.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_5522\" style=\"width: 624px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/writeroom-screenshot.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5522 \" title=\"Writeroom\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/writeroom-screenshot-1024x640.png\" alt=\"Writeroom\" width=\"614\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/writeroom-screenshot-1024x640.png 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/writeroom-screenshot-300x187.png 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/writeroom-screenshot.png 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 614px) 100vw, 614px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Writeroom</p></div>\n<p>After I got bored of the <em>OMG look at my screen! It&#8217;s so geeky and just like those old terminals! wow</em> I stopped using WriteRoom and went back to notebooks. Opening it right now almos tmade my eyes bleed. (granted, I have version 2.5.1 and the new one is 3.x.x, things have changed)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/stypi-the-perfect-blogging-tool/swizec/3312\">For a while I was using Stypi</a> and thought that was the best thing since sliced toast prepared by a wonderful female.</p>\n<div style=\"width: 609px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"    \" title=\"My post on Stypi in Stypi\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Screen-Shot-2012-01-03-at-4.25.36-PM.png\" alt=\"My post on Stypi in Stypi\" width=\"599\" height=\"427\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">My post on Stypi in Stypi</p></div>\n<p>Stypi, again, fell into disuses. Not sure why or how, just did. Then I remembered I had iA Writer installed on my <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"IPad\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IPad\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">iPad</a>.</p>\n<h2>iA Writer</h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_5531\" style=\"width: 624px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-macos.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5531 \" title=\"iA Writer on my laptop\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-macos-1024x640.png\" alt=\"iA Writer on my laptop\" width=\"614\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-macos-1024x640.png 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-macos-300x187.png 300w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-macos.png 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 614px) 100vw, 614px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">iA Writer on my laptop</p></div>\n<p>iA Writer is one of those tools that is just perfect. It does everything I need and nothing more.</p>\n<p>When I started writing on <a href=\"https://leanpub.com/nightowls\" target=\"_blank\">Why programmers work at night</a> I discovered something interesting &#8211; writing in <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Emacs\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emacs\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">Emacs</a> is impossible. It&#8217;s a wonderful markdown editor, great support, awesome <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Syntax highlighting\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Syntax_highlighting\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">syntax highlighting</a>, distractionless coding because there&#8217;s no toolbars and crap and so on.</p>\n<p>I love you Emacs, you glorious bastard, but you suck for writing prose.</p>\n<p>The only place I feel comfortable enough to write is iA Writer. Somewhere between filling up my whole screen with writing, having a super huge font and juuust the perfect kerning and line spacing, iA Writer made me fall in love.</p>\n<p>Syncing across devices via <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"ICloud\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ICloud\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">iCloud</a> or <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Dropbox\" href=\"http://www.crunchbase.com/company/dropbox\" rel=\"crunchbase\" target=\"_blank\">Dropbox</a> was just icing on the cake.</p>\n<p>I think my favourite feature is that once you start typing on a bluetooth keyboard all the controls disappear. Your iPad turns into a blank piece of paper and you&#8217;re going to town on it. Really wonderful.</p>\n<p>Most importantly I can now write in the same environment in a coffee shop, up on a mountain or at my desk.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_5528\" style=\"width: 624px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-ipad-landscape.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5528 \" title=\"iA Writer on the iPad\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-ipad-landscape.png\" alt=\"iA Writer on the iPad\" width=\"614\" height=\"461\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-ipad-landscape.png 1024w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-ipad-landscape-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 614px) 100vw, 614px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">iA Writer on the iPad</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_5529\" style=\"width: 394px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-iphone.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5529 \" title=\"iA Writer on iPhone\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-iphone.png\" alt=\"iA Writer on iPhone\" width=\"384\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-iphone.png 640w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-iphone-200x300.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 384px) 100vw, 384px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">iA Writer on <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"IPhone\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IPhone\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">iPhone</a></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_5530\" style=\"width: 471px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-ipad-portrait-clean.png\"><img class=\" wp-image-5530 \" title=\"iA Writer on iPad once typing begins\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-ipad-portrait-clean.png\" alt=\"iA Writer on iPad once typing begins\" width=\"461\" height=\"614\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-ipad-portrait-clean.png 768w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/ia-writer-ipad-portrait-clean-225x300.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 461px) 100vw, 461px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">iA Writer on iPad once typing begins</p></div>\n<h6 class=\"zemanta-related-title\" style=\"font-size: 1em;\">Related articles</h6>\n<ul class=\"zemanta-article-ul zemanta-article-ul-image\" style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; overflow: hidden;\">\n<li class=\"zemanta-article-ul-li-image zemanta-article-ul-li\" style=\"padding: 0; background: none; list-style: none; display: block; float: left; vertical-align: top; text-align: left; width: 84px; font-size: 11px; margin: 2px 10px 10px 2px;\"><a style=\"box-shadow: 0px 0px 4px #999; padding: 2px; display: block; border-radius: 2px; text-decoration: none;\" href=\"http://www.tuaw.com/2012/10/31/nanowrimo-tools-for-apple-devices-and-a-few-hot-deals-on-wri/\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; border: 0; display: block; width: 80px; max-width: 100%;\" src=\"http://i.zemanta.com/122438801_80_80.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a><a style=\"display: block; overflow: hidden; text-decoration: none; line-height: 12pt; height: 80px; padding: 5px 2px 0 2px;\" href=\"http://www.tuaw.com/2012/10/31/nanowrimo-tools-for-apple-devices-and-a-few-hot-deals-on-wri/\" target=\"_blank\">NaNoWriMo tools for Apple devi